00:49:13,025 --> 00:49:16,768
- I'll save you for later.

844
00:49:16,788 --> 00:49:19,271
(lightning cracks)

845
00:49:19,290 --> 00:49:21,958
(sharp exhale)

846
00:50:22,762 --> 00:50:24,687
- If you woke up
