00:55:32,813 --> 00:55:33,954
- Yep.
- Appreciate it.

885
00:55:40,654 --> 00:55:41,912
Did you go outside already?

886
00:55:42,064 --> 00:55:42,796
- Huh?

887
00:55:43,916 --> 00:55:44,748
