00:56:09,200 --> 00:56:10,440
- Just be quick.

901
00:56:10,593 --> 00:56:11,200
You don't get to be
struck by lightning

902
00:56:11,276 --> 00:56:12,183
Or drowned in a puddle.

903
00:56:12,203 --> 00:56:13,260
- Okay, I'll do my best, okay?

904
00:56:13,278 --> 00:56:14,036
- Okay.

905
