00:58:40,851 --> 00:58:41,742
- Yes.

947
00:58:41,744 --> 00:58:42,684
- Good. Start.

948
00:58:45,839 --> 00:58:49,191
(intense dramatic music)

949
00:58:54,532 --> 00:58:59,493
- One, two, three, four,
five, six, seven, eight.

