of moments of silence,

968
00:59:52,072 --> 00:59:53,905
Which is what we wanted.

969
00:59:53,924 --> 00:59:55,716
Okay, let's do
this. Camera on me.

970
00:59:57,502 --> 00:59:59,077
Red button.

971
00:59:59,096 --> 00:59:59,928
Okay.

972
01:00:00,005 --> 01:00:01,597
And, action.

973
01:00:04,101 --> 01:00:05,601
- Oh god.

